---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | What If Now"
  description="How What If Now collects, uses, and protects your personal data. Plain English. GDPR compliant."
  noindex={false}
>
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy pt-32 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block text-teal font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Privacy Policy</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white font-serif leading-tight mb-4">
        Your privacy.<br />Plain and simple.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        We believe you should know exactly what we collect, why we collect it, and what we do with it. No legalese. No small print.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-6">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <main class="bg-off-white py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-12">

      <!-- What we collect -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">What we collect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
          When you complete the AI Readiness Assessment, we collect:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy">Your name</strong> — to address your results email</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy">Work email address</strong> — to send you your toolkit and results</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy">Company name</strong> — to reference in your results email</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy">Sector and business size</strong> — to provide relevant sector context in your results</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy">Quiz answers</strong> — to calculate your AI readiness score</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We don't collect payment information, sensitive personal data, or anything not listed above.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Why we collect it -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">Why we collect it</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We use your data to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Email you a results summary and a link to download the free AI Readiness Toolkit</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Follow up with relevant content about AI for Irish businesses — we may send occasional emails, and you can unsubscribe any time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Improve the assessment by analysing aggregated, anonymised results</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Our legal basis for processing is <strong class="text-navy">legitimate interest</strong> — you've asked us for something and we're delivering it, along with follow-up that's directly relevant to that request.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Who we share it with -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">Who we share it with</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We share your data with two service providers:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm" style="border-left: 4px solid #2EC4B6;">
            <p class="font-bold text-navy mb-1">Resend</p>
            <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Email delivery service. We send your name, email address, and results summary to Resend solely to deliver your toolkit email. Resend does not use this data for any other purpose.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm" style="border-left: 4px solid #2EC4B6;">
            <p class="font-bold text-navy mb-1">Formspree</p>
            <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Form processing service. Your submission details are stored via Formspree to help us follow up and improve the assessment. Formspree does not use this data for third-party marketing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We do <strong class="text-navy">not</strong> sell your data. We do not share it with data brokers, advertising networks, or third-party marketing platforms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- How long we keep it -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">How long we keep it</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
          We keep your data for <strong class="text-navy">2 years</strong> from the date you completed the assessment, or until you ask us to delete it — whichever comes first. After that, it's gone.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Your rights -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Under GDPR, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {[
            { right: 'Access', desc: 'Request a copy of everything we hold about you' },
            { right: 'Rectification', desc: 'Ask us to correct inaccurate data' },
            { right: 'Erasure', desc: 'Ask us to delete your data entirely' },
            { right: 'Portability', desc: 'Receive your data in a portable format' },
            { right: 'Objection', desc: 'Object to us processing your data' },
            { right: 'Restriction', desc: 'Ask us to limit how we use your data' },
          ].map(({ right, desc }) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
              <p class="font-bold text-navy mb-1">{right}</p>
              <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mt-6">
          To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@whatifnow.ie" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">hello@whatifnow.ie</a>. We'll respond within 30 days.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mt-3">
          You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Irish Data Protection Commission at <a href="https://www.dataprotection.ie" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">dataprotection.ie</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy font-serif mb-4">Contact us</h2>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Questions about this policy? Get in touch.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <a href="mailto:hello@whatifnow.ie" class="text-teal font-bold text-lg hover:underline">hello@whatifnow.ie</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate text-sm mt-1">What If Now · Dublin, Ireland</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
